										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Welcome to WordStream by LOCALiQ!</p>
<p>If you’re a regular reader of the WordStream blog, you might have noticed that things look a little bit different here this week. Good eye! That’s because we’ve given the site a new look to match our new mission: WordStream is now <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/about-us">WordStream by LOCALiQ</a>, and together, we’re more committed than ever to being your go-to source for data and insights in the world of digital marketing.</p>
<p>Since 2018, WordStream and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/about-localiq">LOCALiQ</a> have been part of the same family, and now we’re evolving our brand to show how closely knit we really are. Going forward, WordStream remains your source for industry news, trends, and in-depth marketing and advertising advice, while LOCALiQ provides the <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/marketing-services">platform, technology and services</a> that allow our clients’ businesses to thrive.</p>
<p>What does this mean for you? Rest assured we’re going to keep bringing you tons of <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog-search?category=marketing-ideas">creative marketing ideas</a> and actionable tips to save you time and money on your online ad campaigns – plus free tools like our <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/google-adwords?cid=Web_blog_InContentTextLink">Google Ads Performance Grader</a> and <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/keywords?cid=Web_Blog_InContentTextLink_FKT">Free Keyword Tool</a> to make planning and analysis easier.</p>
<p>So what’s different?</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>A cleaner, faster, more accessible design</strong> that is easier to navigate on both desktop and mobile devices.</li>
<li><strong>Deeper connections</strong> between WordStream and LOCALiQ, so you can find the help you need, whether you’re a small business owner wearing multiple hats, or you’re a specialist diving deep into paid search, social media, and other marketing channels.</li>
<li><strong>More resources</strong> to help you meet your goals, from our popular blogs to free guides and learning hubs, like <a href="https://localiq.com/local-marketing-lab" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LOCALiQ Marketing Lab</a>, and new free tools, like the <a href="https://localiq.com/localiq-grader/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LOCALiQ Online Presence Grader</a>.</li>
</ul>
<p>We encourage you to take a look around at the new WordStream, and spend some time with <a href="https://localiq.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LOCALiQ</a> as well. Our #1 goal is still to help you grow your business, and we know small businesses still have big goals. We started small ourselves, over a decade ago, so we’ve been on the same journey. We’re excited to continue the journey with you. Please let us know what you think!</p>
<p>P.S. Huge thanks to all the people who worked tirelessly to bring this new site to life, especially the web team (Justin Al-Qudah, Loni Walker, and John Parks), the content team (Kristen McCormick, Steph Heitman, Gordon Donnelly, and Susie Marino), our designer Alex Niemeyer, and our brand leader Gina Kaiser.</p>
