					<description><![CDATA[<p>What are the most expensive keywords in the United Kingdom? These 25 keywords will cost you more British pounds per click than any other keywords in AdWords advertising...</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.wordstream.com/blog/ws/2017/06/28/most-expensive-keywords-uk-edition">The Most Expensive Keywords in the UK</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.wordstream.com">WordStream</a>.</p>
